00:35:31.050 --> 00:35:31.820
Merezco un castigo.

00:35:32.460 --> 00:35:33.020
¡Vengan!

00:35:33.650 --> 00:35:34.500
Para Yuan Buqu,

00:35:35.340 --> 00:35:36.300
